[normal] will be of practical use to 
[normal]Commissioner
[normal]s.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]              
[normal]Quality Standards for Dermatology
[normal]; 
[normal]providing the right care for people with skin conditions
[normal] 
[normal]is a 
[normal]multi
[normal]-
[normal]stakeholder 
[normal](including the BAD) 
[normal]publication 
[normal]and is available on the PCC website and has implications for commissioning
