[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]5.4
[normal]              
[normal]Recognition of multi-disciplinary care pathways 
[normal]should be highlighted to 
[normal]Commissioner
[normal]s 
[normal]considering
[normal] services with a high level of multi
[normal]ple morbidities
[normal] 
[normal]in certain
[normal] patient groups. Within the NHS flexibility
[normal] and integration have evolved
[normal] around on-call services and in-patient consultations – if these services are 
